comments: Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Camborne Redruth.

Created 1.4.1934 out of the parishes of Camborne, Redruth, Illogan, 
    Gwennap and Wendron. Abolished 1.4.1974 to become the Kerrier unparished area. 
    See also Table 2, notes (b) and (e).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Phillack in Phillack 
    Urban District. Abolished 1.10.1935 and added to the parish of Hayle. See 
    also Table 2, note (c).
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Gwinear Gwithian

Created 1.4.1934 from the separate parishes of Gwinear and Gwithian. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Gwinear Gwithian

That part which until 1.10.1935 formed the parishes of East 
    Phillack and West Phillack. See 
    also Table 2, note (c).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Camborne Redruth 
    and St. Agnes. See also Table 2, note (e).

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of East Phillack 
    and West Phillack.
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Camborne Redruth.

That part which until 1.4.1934 formed the parish of Illogan. 
    See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Phillack in Hayle 
    Urban District. Abolished 1.10.1935 and added to the parish of Hayle. See 
    also Table 2, note (c).
